(165, 3, 3, 'Radiant and pure, in light divine,'),
(165, 3, 4, 'The building of our God.'),
(165, 4, 1, 'Then rest, divinely sweet,'),
(165, 4, 2, 'Our pilgrim feet shall know;'),
