(178, 2, 2, 'Where all around in bliss,'),
(178, 2, 3, 'Where all in Thee supremely blest,'),
(178, 2, 4, 'Thy praise their service is.'),
(178, 3, 1, 'Eternal love their portion is,'),
(178, 3, 2, 'Where love has found its rest;'),
(178, 3, 3, 'And, filled with Thee, the constant mind'),
