(271, 4, 3, 'Then on our gladdened vision burst'),
(271, 4, 4, 'God\'s shady, cool retreat.'),
(271, 5, 1, 'The manna and the springing well'),
(271, 5, 2, 'Suffice for every need;'),
(271, 5, 3, 'And Eshcol\'s grapes the story tell'),
