(283, 3, 3, 'We taste of heav\'nly joys with Thee - how blest!'),
(283, 3, 4, 'Thine own heart satisfied, and ours at rest.'),
(284, 1, 1, '\"Not of the world\" - blest words of Christ the Lord'),
