(391, 3, 4, 'Waiting our heavenly part.'),
(391, 4, 1, 'Spring up, O Spirit most gracious!'),
(391, 4, 2, 'Teach us while pilgrims below'),
(391, 4, 3, 'More of God\'s glorious greatness,'),
