(398, 4, 4, 'Where Thou shalt ever be adored.'),
(398, 5, 1, 'And now in faith and hope and love,'),
(398, 5, 2, 'We wait to greet Thee from above;'),
(398, 5, 3, 'Each heart sustained in power and grace,'),
